high_descs: Go to the desk directly behind you.
Pick up the disc from the left front corner of the desk.
Turn right and carry the disc to the white safe in the corner to your left.
Put the disc in the safe.
Return to the desk.
Get the disc from the far right side of the desk.
Carry the disc to the corner safe.
Put the disc into the safe and close the safe.
anns.task_desc: Secure two discs in a bedroom safe.

high_descs: Turn right towards the window and turn right towards the desk.
Pick up the CD from the desk.
Turn right towards the bed, turn left towards the bin, turn right towards the vault on your left.
Place the CD in the vault.
Turn left towards the bed and then turn right towards the desk.
Pick up the CD from the desk.
Turn right towards the bed, turn left towards the bin, turn right towards the vault on your left.
Place the CD in the vault and close.
anns.task_desc: Transfer the two CDs from the desk into the vault.

high_descs: Move to the desk closest to the widow.
Pick up the CD from the desk.
Move to the safe to the right of you to the left of the mirror.
Place the CD inside and close the door.
Move to the desk closest to the widow.
Pick up the CD from the desk.
Move to the safe to the right of you to the left of the mirror.
Place the CD inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put the two CDs on the desk closest to the window in the safe.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the desk.
Pick up the CD on the left.
Turn right and cross the room to the trashcan, and turn left and head to the safe.
Put the CD in the safe.
Turn around and head to the trashcan, then turn right and cross the room to the chair.
Face the desk and pick up the CD.
Turn right and cross the room to the trashcan, then turn left and head to the safe.
Put the CD in the safe.
anns.task_desc: Put two CDs in the safe.

high_descs: Turn around so you are next to the wall and facing the blue chair
Pick up the CD off of the desk
Maneuver your way to the left of the bed so you are facing the wall to the left of the floor safe
Open the safe and put the CD inside it, before closing it again
Turn back towards the desk, but this time stand to the right of where you stood last time
Pick up another CD off of the desk
Head back to the safe
Open the safe and put the other CD inside it, before closing it again
anns.task_desc: Put two CD's in the safe
